{
  "texts": [
    "The concept of \"virtual legal personality\" is introduced and the status of virtual avatars as agents of actions in the digital space is regulated.Legal regulation also covers aspects of mental impact, cyber-physical consequences and content liability.",
    "Standards for the safe use of VR/AR devices, restrictions for vulnerable categories of persons, ethical standards of immersion, and rules of digital behaviour in an immersive environment are defined.Module XI is key to shaping the concept of \"virtual ethics\", protecting personal data in deeply interactive environments, and developing legislation that regulates the hybrid reality of physical, digital and emotional-cognitive dimensions.",
    "Module XII.",
    "Legal regulation of the MetaverseModule XII establishes a regulatory model for governing the Metaverse as interactive virtual environments powered by immersive technologies, blockchain infrastructures, and artificial intelligence algorithms.",
    "The goal is to form a legal framework for activities in decentralized virtual spaces [16].The concepts of digital territoriality, tokenized jurisdiction, virtual citizenship, and contract reality are introduced."
  ]
}